<h1><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:
background1'>斗十四规则<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></h1>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;
mso-themecolor:background1'>1</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>、游戏介绍<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>斗十四由<span
lang=EN-US>21</span>种牌组成，红牌<span lang=EN-US>12</span>种，黑牌<span lang=EN-US>9</span>种，每种牌型<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>张，共<span lang=EN-US>84</span>张。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;
mso-themecolor:background1'>2</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>、点数计算<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>全红牌：算两头点数之和<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>黑牌： 无点数<span
lang=EN-US><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;mso-pagination:widow-orphan'><span
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>红黑牌：只算一头的红点数<span
lang=EN-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;
mso-themecolor:background1'>3</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>、番数计算<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>五门红（天、地、人、和、幺四）：拉（碰<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>张）<span lang=EN-US>1</span>番，拉并手中有<span lang=EN-US>1</span>张（共计<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>张）<span lang=EN-US>2</span>番<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>其他牌：拉并手中有<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>张（共计<span lang=EN-US>4</span>张）<span lang=EN-US>1</span>番<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left;text-indent:5.25pt;
mso-char-indent-count:.5'><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>报胡：<span lang=EN-US>1</span>番（所有人偷牌结束后，手中点数达到<span
lang=EN-US>30</span>点可选择报胡，报胡后，牌型不可改变，不允许拉）<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>天胡、地胡：<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>番<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;</span></span><span style='font-family:宋体;
mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>红胡、黑胡：封顶计算<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;
mso-themecolor:background1'>4</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>、操作说明<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>漂：摸牌前选择漂，漂后底分翻倍。<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>吃：只要两张牌相加等于十四点，即可用一张去吃另一张。<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>拉：拉牌即碰牌，拉了以后要偷一张牌。<span lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=left style='text-align:left'><span style='font-family:
宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>偷：</span><span style='font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:
宋体;color:white;mso-themecolor:background1'>从底牌拿一张放手上，不可公开，故为偷，出现在拉牌或摸到丁丁斧头之后。<span
lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>


